Pictures can be deceiving, but from what I see here, that's hardly
even worth worrying about.

Clean up the failed undercoating. Failed undercoating is a water trap
that will accelerate rust. So get the area cleaned up down to bare
metal, trim up the jagged lower edge, and treat with Rust Bullet.

John

